{"word":"H4057 - מִדְבָּר - midbâr - mid-bawr' - Desert","slug":"H4057","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מִדְבָּר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>midbâr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mid-bawr'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Desert"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D3;&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05E8; - midba&#x0302;r</b> - <i>mid-bawr'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H1696\">H1696</a> in the sense of <i>driving</i>; a <i>pasture</i> (that is, open field, whither cattle are driven); by implication a <i>desert</i>; also <i>speech</i> (including its organs): - desert, south, speech, wilderness."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1682\">H1682</a>, <a href=\"#/H1683\">H1683</a>, <a href=\"#/H1687\">H1687</a>, <a href=\"#/H1688\">H1688</a>, <a href=\"#/H1696\">H1696</a>, <a href=\"#/H1697\">H1697</a>, <a href=\"#/H1698\">H1698</a>, <a href=\"#/H1699\">H1699</a>, <a href=\"#/H1700\">H1700</a>, <a href=\"#/H1702\">H1702</a>, <a href=\"#/H1703\">H1703</a>, <a href=\"#/H1704\">H1704</a>, <a href=\"#/H1705\">H1705</a>"}]}